1C111 Propellants and constituent chemicals for propellants, other than those specified in 1C011, as follows:
1C111.a Propulsive substances:
1C111.a.1 Spherical or spheroidal aluminium powder other than that specified in the Military Goods Controls, in particle size of less than 200 μm and an aluminium content of 97 % by weight or more, if at least 10 % of the total weight is made up of particles of less than 63 μm, according to ISO 2591-1:1988 or national equivalents;
