3A228.b.2 Rated for a peak current of 500 A or more;
3A228.c Modules or assemblies with a fast switching function, other than those specified in 3A001.g. or 3A001.h., having all of the following characteristics:
3A228.c.1 Anode peak voltage rating greater than 2 kV;
3A228.c.2 Anode peak current rating of 500 A or more; and
3A228.c.3 Turn-on time of 1 μs or less.

