3A229 N.B. SEE ALSO MILITARY GOODS CONTROLS.
3A229.a Detonator firing sets (initiator systems, firesets), including electronically-charged, explosively-driven and optically-driven firing sets, other than those specified in 1A007.a., designed to drive multiple controlled detonators specified in 1A007.b.;
3A229.b Modular electrical pulse generators (pulsers) having all of the following characteristics:
