3A229.b.2 Capable of delivering their energy in less than 15 μs into loads of less than 40 ohms;
3A229.b.3 Having an output greater than 100 A;
3A229.b.4 No dimension greater than 30 cm;
3A229.b.5 Weight less than 30 kg; and
3A229.b.6 Specified for use over an extended temperature range 223 K (-50 °C) to 373 K (100 °C) or specified as suitable for aerospace applications.
