3B501 Equipment for the manufacturing of semiconductor devices or materials, as follows and specially designed components and accessories therefor:
3B501.a Equipment designed for epitaxial growth as follows:
3B501.a.4 Equipment designed for epitaxial growth of silicon (Si) or silicon germanium (SiGe), and having all of the following:
3B501.a.4.a At least one preclean chamber designed to provide a surface preparation means to clean the surface of the wafer; and
