5B001.a Note: 5B001.a. does not control optical fibre characterization equipment.
5B001.b Equipment and specially designed components or accessories therefor, specially designed for the "development" of any of the following telecommunication transmission or switching equipment:
5B001.b.1 Not used;
5B001.b.2 Equipment employing a "laser" and having any of the following:
