5B001.b.2.b Not used;
5B001.b.2.c Not used;
5B001.b.2.d Employing analogue techniques and having a bandwidth exceeding 2,5 GHz; or
5B001.b.2.d Note: 5B001.b.2.d. does not control equipment specially designed for the "development" of commercial TV systems.
5B001.b.3 Not used;
