8A002.i.1.b Tactile sense between the manipulator and an external object; or
8A002.i.2 Controlled by proportional master-slave techniques and having 5 degrees of 'freedom of movement' or more;
8A002.i.2 Technical Note: For the purposes of 8A002.i.2., only functions having proportionally related motion control using positional feedback are counted when determining the number of degrees of 'freedom of movement'.
8A002.j Air independent power systems specially designed for underwater use, as follows:
