8A002.j.2.b Systems specially designed to use a monoatomic gas;
8A002.j.2.c Devices or enclosures, specially designed for underwater noise reduction in frequencies below 10 kHz, or special mounting devices for shock mitigation; and
8A002.j.2.d Specially designed exhaust systems that do not exhaust continuously the products of combustion;
8A002.j.3 "Fuel cell" air independent power systems with an output exceeding 2 kW and having any of the following:
8A002.j.3.a Devices or enclosures, specially designed for underwater noise reduction in frequencies below 10 kHz, or special mounting devices for shock mitigation; or
8A002.j.3.b Systems having all of the following:
8A002.j.3.b.1 Specially designed to pressurise the products of reaction or for fuel reformation;
8A002.j.3.b.2 Specially designed to store the products of the reaction; and
8A002.j.3.b.3 Specially designed to discharge the products of the reaction against a pressure of 100 kPa or more;
8A002.j.4 Stirling cycle engine air independent power systems having all of the following:
